= Use
Automatically enable the numeric keypad on the login screen when using Plasma Login Manager as the system's display manager (login manager)

= How to use
```bash
git clone https://github.com/bailuocf/plm-numlock.git
cd ~/plm-numlock
./plm-numlock.sh
``` 
